            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Aux mers d'azur où nagent les étoiles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Notre œil de chair se noie en se plongeant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Mais l'infini parfois lève ses voiles",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Pour notre esprit, cet œil intelligent.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Peuples du ciel, les astres ont une âme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Leur tourbillon peut jouir ou souffrir,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "L'amour unit tous ces frères de flamme :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Pleurez, soleils, un globe va mourir !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Aux mers d'azur où nagent les étoiles,\nNotre œil de chair se noie en se plongeant,\nMais l'infini parfois lève ses voiles\nPour notre esprit, cet œil intelligent.\nPeuples du ciel, les astres ont une âme,\nLeur tourbillon peut jouir ou souffrir,\nL'amour unit tous ces frères de flamme :\nPleurez, soleils, un globe va mourir !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Il pivotait dans son noble équilibre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Pour que jamais on n'y connût la faim.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "L'homme groupé pouvait, heureux et libre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Tirer de lui des récoltes sans fin.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Mais ses erreurs ont causé ses désastres,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Sous la contrainte il s'est laissé pourrir,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "De son typhus il gangrène les astres,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Pleurez, soleils, un globe va mourir !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il pivotait dans son noble équilibre,\nPour que jamais on n'y connût la faim.\nL'homme groupé pouvait, heureux et libre,\nTirer de lui des récoltes sans fin.\nMais ses erreurs ont causé ses désastres,\nSous la contrainte il s'est laissé pourrir,\nDe son typhus il gangrène les astres,\nPleurez, soleils, un globe va mourir !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Fleuve de sang, la guerre s'y promène,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "L'Idée y porte un bâillon outrageant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "L'anthropophage y vit de chair humaine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "De chair humaine y vit l'homme d'argent.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "C'est le bourreau qui, dans ses mains infâmes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Porte ce globe et qui semble l'offrir",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Au Dieu vengeur, au dieu bourreau des âmes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Pleurez, soleils, un globe va mourir !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Fleuve de sang, la guerre s'y promène,\nL'Idée y porte un bâillon outrageant,\nL'anthropophage y vit de chair humaine,\nDe chair humaine y vit l'homme d'argent.\nC'est le bourreau qui, dans ses mains infâmes,\nPorte ce globe et qui semble l'offrir\nAu Dieu vengeur, au dieu bourreau des âmes,\nPleurez, soleils, un globe va mourir !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Pourtant le code est écrit dans nos veines ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "L'attrait conduit les esprits et les corps.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Du grand concert des volontés humaines",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Les passions sont les divins accords.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Non, le poids ment ! l'âme à tort se dilate,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "En amputant la hache croit guérir :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "De Prométhée on fait un cul-de-jatte !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Pleurez, soleils, un globe va mourir !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pourtant le code est écrit dans nos veines ;\nL'attrait conduit les esprits et les corps.\nDu grand concert des volontés humaines\nLes passions sont les divins accords.\nNon, le poids ment ! l'âme à tort se dilate,\nEn amputant la hache croit guérir :\nDe Prométhée on fait un cul-de-jatte !\nPleurez, soleils, un globe va mourir !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "On entendra comme un sanglot qui navre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Dernier soupir du condamné géant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "L'Éternité prendra ce grand cadavre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Pour l'enfouir aux fosses du néant.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Les univers, au sein des nuits profondes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Cherchant ses os les pourront découvrir",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Au champ de lait, cimetière des mondes.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Pleurez, soleils, un globe va mourir !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "On entendra comme un sanglot qui navre,\nDernier soupir du condamné géant,\nL'Éternité prendra ce grand cadavre\nPour l'enfouir aux fosses du néant.\nLes univers, au sein des nuits profondes,\nCherchant ses os les pourront découvrir\nAu champ de lait, cimetière des mondes.\nPleurez, soleils, un globe va mourir !"
        }
